        "rich_text_FxMxqa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>If you are looking for fashion forward designs for everyday wear, 9kt gold is the way to go! Whether you are looking for 9kt gold earrings or bracelet gold, 9kt jewelry is perfect if you are looking for accessible and durable daily wear jewelry. </p>",
